      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COMPTON TO AVOID (1) has recorded back to back wins, last time scoring at Mt Gambier over 305m by 2.5 lengths (17.49). Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Great chance to get the job done again. CANYA FEEL IT (8) looks close to win after hitting the frame last run (22.95) at this track in a Grade 6. Has first look at box 8 this time. Expected to be in this for a long way. AGENT TWENTY ONE (4) is a well performed sprinter ideally suited at the shorter trips. Last start placegetter over 300m at this track in a Grade 6 (17.00). Has never missed the frame at the trip from five starts. Well placed and gets his chance. MEG'S CHARM (2) is worth including.",
